# Sensitive files - NEVER commit
**/.ssh/id_*
**/.ssh/*.pem
**/.ssh/known_hosts
**/*.key
**/*.pem

# Credentials
**/.netrc
**/.npmrc
**/.pypirc
**/credentials*
**/*token*
**/*secret*
!packages/claude/.claude/rules/secrets.md
**/.env
**/.env.*

# Local overrides
*.local
# ...except the tmux persistence config — versioned + shared across machines
!packages/tmux/.tmux.conf.local
.local/
**/rules/local.md
**/config.local.toml
**/.vagrant/

# OS junk
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# Editor
*.swp
*.swo
*~
.idea/
.vscode/
